TT gets the closest a Rhino can to a disqusted look.

TT:  He was found guilty of spying and high treason and got a life 
sentence.  I didn't totally believe it myself.....at least not until a 
group of Predicons helped him escape from prison.  What happened after 
that is none of your business.

He felt the vile stored inside his body.

TT: remember that, and DON'T mention it again.
